com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.baseclasses

Class Passphrase<PassphraseRepresentation>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.baseclasses.Passphrase<PassphraseRepresentation>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NoSecurity, Password, Pattern, Pin

    public abstract class Passphrase<PassphraseRepresentation>
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by aravind on 10/8/14. Abstract class to represent a generic passphrase. Any class can be used for PassphraseRepresentation, but the subclasses should provide a one-one mapping from any object of PassphraseRepresentation to a set of unique Strings.
